##Verify Router visibility
ping 10.10.2.2
ping 10.10.3.3

@R1
router bgp 65001
bgp log-neighbor-changes

neighbor 10.10.2.2 remote-as 65002
neighbor 10.10.3.3 remote-as 65003

!Because we are peering via loopbacks
neighbor 10.10.2.2 update-source loopback0
neighbor 10.10.3.3 update-source loopback0

!Advertise R1 loopback
network 10.10.1.1 mask 255.255.255.255

@R2
router bgp 65002
bgp log-neighbor-changes

neighbor 10.10.1.1 remote-as 65001
neighbor 10.10.3.3 remote-as 65003

neighbor 10.10.1.1 update-source loopback0
neighbor 10.10.3.3 update-source loopback0

network 10.10.2.2 mask 255.255.255.255

@R3
router bgp 65003
bgp log-neighbor-changes

neighbor 10.10.1.1 remote-as 65001
neighbor 10.10.2.2 remote-as 65002

neighbor 10.10.1.1 update-source loopback0
neighbor 10.10.2.2 update-source loopback0

network 10.10.3.3 mask 255.255.255.255

